### Get all pizzas
GET https://localhost:5001/api/pizzas

### Get a specific pizza
GET https://localhost:5001/api/pizzas/1

### Create a new pizza
POST https://localhost:5001/api/pizzas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Margherita",
  "isGlutenFree": false
}

### Update an existing pizza
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/pizzas/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Pepperoni",
  "isGlutenFree": true
}

### Delete a pizza
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/pizzas/1
